- <i>I do believe in fairies.! I do.! I do.!</i>
- He's alive!

01:17:44.607 --> 01:17:47.838
Oh, help.
It's Hook or me this time.

01:17:47.910 --> 01:17:49.673
[Chattering]

01:17:50.780 --> 01:17:53.146
Why is he? What is he?

01:17:53.216 --> 01:17:55.410
<i>I'll have one last story</i>
<i>before you die.</i>

01:17:55.483 --> 01:17:57.417
<i>The story of Peter Pan.</i>

01:17:57.485 --> 01:17:59.510
[Gasps]

01:17:59.588 --> 01:18:02.079
Once upon a time...
Once upon a time...

01:18:02.157 --> 01:18:06.559
Brutes, Red-Handed Jill
is gonna tell us a story.

01:18:06.627 --> 01:18:09.425
[All Cheering]
There was a boy
named Peter Pan...

01:18:09.496 --> 01:18:12.260
<i>who decided</i>
<i>not to grow up.</i>

01:18:12.333 --> 01:18:15.733
[Gasps]
Skip the prologue.

01:18:15.802 --> 01:18:20.205
So he flew away
to the Neverland
where the pirates are.

01:18:20.273 --> 01:18:23.003
[Gasps]
Was one of them pirates
called Noodler?

01:18:23.076 --> 01:18:25.600
- Yes.
- Captain, did you hear?

01:18:25.677 --> 01:18:29.408
- I am in a story.
- [Boys Screaming]

01:18:29.481 --> 01:18:33.076
What fun he must have had.

01:18:33.151 --> 01:18:35.084
Yes.

01:18:35.152 --> 01:18:38.519
But he was rather lonely.

01:18:38.589 --> 01:18:41.490
Lonely?

01:18:41.559 --> 01:18:43.618
He needed a Wendy.

01:18:43.694 --> 01:18:46.594
- I need a Wendy.
- <i>[Boys Screaming]</i>

01:18:46.663 --> 01:18:48.756
Very exciting.
Two dead already.

01:18:48.832 --> 01:18:52.768
Why a Wendy?
He liked my stories.

01:18:52.836 --> 01:18:56.464
What stories?
<i>Cinderella.</i>

01:18:56.538 --> 01:19:00.474
<i>Snow White. Sleeping Beauty.</i>

01:19:00.542 --> 01:19:02.772
- Love stories?
- [Groaning]

01:19:02.845 --> 01:19:06.541
Adventures in which good
triumphs over evil.

01:19:06.614 --> 01:19:10.072
- [All Cheering]
- They all end in a kiss.

01:19:15.822 --> 01:19:17.756
A kiss.

01:19:19.826 --> 01:19:23.227
He does feel.

01:19:24.864 --> 01:19:27.162
He feels about you.

01:19:27.233 --> 01:19:30.634
<i>[Pirates Yelling]</i>

01:19:30.703 --> 01:19:34.571
She told him stories.
He taught her to fly.

01:19:34.640 --> 01:19:37.403
- How?
- [Snickers]

01:19:37.475 --> 01:19:40.933
You just think happy thoughts.
They lift you into the air.

01:19:41.012 --> 01:19:45.277
Alas, I have no happy thoughts.
That brings you down.

01:19:45.349 --> 01:19:49.342
- [All Gasping]
- How else?

01:19:49.420 --> 01:19:51.012
- No!
- <i>Leave her alone.!</i>

01:19:51.088 --> 01:19:53.750
It's fairy dust.
You need fairy dust!

01:19:53.824 --> 01:19:56.587
<i>[Boys Together]</i>
<i>Michael.!</i>

01:19:56.659 --> 01:19:59.753
[Gasps]
What of Pan?

01:19:59.829 --> 01:20:02.423
Will unhappy thoughts
bring him down?

01:20:02.498 --> 01:20:04.432
He has no unhappy thoughts.

01:20:04.500 --> 01:20:06.626
Aw.

01:20:06.702 --> 01:20:10.263
How if his Wendy
walks the plank!

01:20:10.339 --> 01:20:12.671
[Pirates Cheering]

01:20:12.741 --> 01:20:14.470
<i>[Pirates Chanting]</i>
<i>Plank.! Plank.! Plank.! Plank.!</i>
<i>Plank.! Plank.! Plank.! Plank.!</i>

01:20:16.610 --> 01:20:19.943
Plank! Plank! Plank! Plank!
Plank! Plank! Plank! Plank!

01:20:20.014 --> 01:20:23.472
Plank! Plank! Plank! Plank!
Plank, plank, plank!

01:20:23.551 --> 01:20:26.144
[Chattering]

01:20:26.219 --> 01:20:30.781
<i>You know, I really am</i>
<i>terribly sorry about this.</i>

01:20:30.857 --> 01:20:34.793
- [All Gasping]
- <i>[Ticking]</i>

01:20:37.529 --> 01:20:42.660
The irony.
It comes for Hook...

01:20:42.735 --> 01:20:45.226
and gets a story.

01:20:45.304 --> 01:20:47.863
- [Wendy Screams]
- No!

01:20:47.939 --> 01:20:50.567
[Pirates Laughing]

01:20:50.641 --> 01:20:53.974
- [Screaming]
- No!

01:20:54.045 --> 01:20:57.343
[Snickering]

01:21:00.283 --> 01:21:03.218
Did you hear her
hit the water?

01:21:03.286 --> 01:21:05.220
Because I didn't.

01:21:08.257 --> 01:21:10.350
<i>[Hook]</i>
<i>The beast has swallowed her whole.</i>

01:21:10.426 --> 01:21:14.055
Hmm.
[Both Snickering]

01:21:14.130 --> 01:21:18.896
- Starboard side!
- [Pirates Shouting]

01:21:18.967 --> 01:21:23.836
- It looks for more, Captain.
- Then let's give it more.

01:21:23.905 --> 01:21:26.737
To the plank!
[Cheering]

01:21:26.807 --> 01:21:31.107
- [Boys Protesting]
- Silence, puling spawn!

01:21:31.178 --> 01:21:34.944
[Gasps]
I'll show you the road
to dusty death.

01:21:35.015 --> 01:21:38.916
- [Boys Screaming]
- [Pirates Cheering]

01:21:42.422 --> 01:21:44.356
Huh?

01:21:44.424 --> 01:21:47.392
<i>[Ticking]</i>

01:21:52.030 --> 01:21:54.430
- [Grunts]
- Into the rigging with you!

01:21:54.499 --> 01:21:58.434
Hunt it down!
Move, you scabs!

01:21:58.502 --> 01:22:01.062
[Chattering]

01:22:07.444 --> 01:22:09.935
[Boys Screaming]

01:22:13.850 --> 01:22:16.819
[Boys Gasping, Laughing]

01:22:32.800 --> 01:22:36.292
- [Pirate Shouting]
- [Gasping]

01:22:38.171 --> 01:22:40.105
<i>[Water Splashing]</i>

01:22:40.173 --> 01:22:42.107
What was that?

01:23:09.600 --> 01:23:13.161
<i>[Pirates Chattering]</i>

01:23:13.237 --> 01:23:16.536
<i>It's here, Captain.! Devil.! Demon.!</i>

01:23:16.607 --> 01:23:20.201
<i>Accursed beast.!</i>
<i>Your time is up.!</i>

01:23:20.276 --> 01:23:22.710
Hello.

01:23:25.748 --> 01:23:29.148
[Screams]
<i>[Water Splashing]</i>

01:23:31.386 --> 01:23:35.152
<i>So, Peter Pan.</i>

01:23:39.126 --> 01:23:41.060
This is all your doing.

01:23:41.128 --> 01:23:45.622
Aye, James Hook.
It's all my doing.

01:23:47.768 --> 01:23:50.793
Proud and insolent youth,

01:23:52.939 --> 01:23:55.669
prepare to meet thy doom.

01:23:55.742 --> 01:23:58.369
Have at thee!
[Grunting]

01:24:01.246 --> 01:24:04.647
[Grunting Continues]

01:24:04.716 --> 01:24:08.981
[Pirates Yelling]

01:24:11.222 --> 01:24:15.716
<i>Leave him.! He's mine.</i>

01:24:15.793 --> 01:24:17.693
Now!

01:24:17.762 --> 01:24:21.219
[Boys Yelling]

01:24:23.333 --> 01:24:25.563
[Yells]

01:24:29.905 --> 01:24:32.373
[Grunting]

01:24:33.842 --> 01:24:35.935
[Peter Yells]

01:24:38.980 --> 01:24:40.948
- Uh-uh-uh-uh-uh!
- [Screams]

01:24:41.015 --> 01:24:43.609
[Grunting Continues]

01:24:43.685 --> 01:24:46.051
[Screaming]

01:24:50.591 --> 01:24:54.960
Here you are. Here.
I never wanted to be a pirate anyway.

01:24:55.028 --> 01:24:58.929
I'm gonna spend the rest
of my life doing good works.
[Screaming]

01:25:04.470 --> 01:25:07.268
[Grunts]
I got him!

01:25:07.340 --> 01:25:10.536
[Screaming, Grunts]

01:25:10.942 --> 01:25:12.739
Villain! Ne'er-do-well!

01:25:12.811 --> 01:25:15.109
<i>Libertine.!</i>
[Screaming]

01:25:15.180 --> 01:25:18.809
[Screams, Muffled Chattering]

01:25:22.019 --> 01:25:24.146
<i>[Grunting Continues]</i>

01:25:24.221 --> 01:25:27.156
[Yelling]

01:25:27.224 --> 01:25:31.489
- It's Hook! He flies!
- [Peter Grunts]

01:25:31.561 --> 01:25:34.724
[Grunts]

01:25:34.797 --> 01:25:37.925
And he likes it!

01:25:38.001 --> 01:25:40.969
[Grunting]

01:25:41.036 --> 01:25:43.664
[Laughs]
[Screams, Grunts]

01:25:43.739 --> 01:25:46.003
<i>You want to fly? Let's fly.</i>

01:25:46.074 --> 01:25:50.567
<i>[Peter Laughing]</i>

01:25:50.645 --> 01:25:54.240
Not bad... for an old man.

01:25:54.315 --> 01:25:56.249
[Laughs]

01:25:56.317 --> 01:25:59.081
[Grunts]
[Laughing Continues]

01:25:59.153 --> 01:26:01.143
I know what you are!

01:26:01.221 --> 01:26:03.849
I am the best there ever was!

01:26:03.923 --> 01:26:06.153
You're a tragedy.

01:26:06.226 --> 01:26:09.127
- [Peter Grunts]
- [Hook Screams, Grunts]

01:26:09.195 --> 01:26:11.754
Me? Tragic?

01:26:12.831 --> 01:26:15.766
<i>She was leaving you, Pan.</i>

01:26:17.603 --> 01:26:21.470
Your Wendy was leaving you.

01:26:21.539 --> 01:26:24.201
<i>Why should she stay?</i>

01:26:24.275 --> 01:26:28.974
What have you to offer?
You are incomplete.

01:26:29.047 --> 01:26:32.345
She'd rather grow up
than stay with you.

01:26:32.416 --> 01:26:34.441
[Grunts]

01:26:37.921 --> 01:26:40.821
Let us now take a peep
into the future.

01:26:40.890 --> 01:26:44.724
[Yelling]
<i>What's this I see?</i>
<i>'Tis the fair Wendy.</i>

01:26:44.794 --> 01:26:49.231
<i>She's in her nursery.</i>
<i>The window's shut.</i>

01:26:49.298 --> 01:26:52.789
I'll open it!
[Grunting]

01:26:52.867 --> 01:26:56.132
I'm afraid the window's barred.
I'll call out her name.

01:26:56.204 --> 01:26:58.138
She can't hear you.
No!

01:26:58.206 --> 01:27:00.333
She can't see you.
Wendy!

01:27:00.407 --> 01:27:04.036
She's forgotten all about you.
Stop! Please! Stop it!

01:27:05.713 --> 01:27:08.238
And what is this I see?

01:27:08.315 --> 01:27:13.183
[Panting]
There is another in your place.

01:27:13.252 --> 01:27:17.916
<i>He is called... husband.</i>

01:27:19.726 --> 01:27:23.593
[Grunts]
[Yells, Grunts]

01:27:23.662 --> 01:27:26.927
[All Grunting]

01:27:26.998 --> 01:27:30.161
[Panting]

01:27:54.857 --> 01:27:57.553
[Grunts]

01:27:57.626 --> 01:28:00.789
[Screams]
<i>[Boy]</i>
<i>No.! Peter.!</i>

01:28:00.863 --> 01:28:04.229
[Grunts]

01:28:04.298 --> 01:28:06.926
[Screams, Gasps]

01:28:07.001 --> 01:28:09.401
You die alone...

01:28:09.470 --> 01:28:12.905
and unloved.

01:28:14.107 --> 01:28:16.473
Unloved.

01:28:21.148 --> 01:28:23.081
Just like me.

01:28:27.520 --> 01:28:30.580
- No!
- No!

01:28:50.974 --> 01:28:53.168
[Yelling]

01:28:55.077 --> 01:28:57.568
[Screaming]

01:29:01.651 --> 01:29:04.642
- <i>[Boys Shouting]</i>
- Silence, all,

01:29:04.719 --> 01:29:08.052
<i>for Wendy's farewell.</i>

01:29:10.959 --> 01:29:13.358
Peter.

01:29:16.096 --> 01:29:18.724
I'm sorry. I must grow up.

01:29:20.401 --> 01:29:25.337
But... this is yours.

01:29:27.340 --> 01:29:30.275
[Grunts]
'Tis just a thimble.

01:29:32.111 --> 01:29:34.977
[Scoffs]
How like a girl!

01:29:35.047 --> 01:29:39.643
- [Pirates Laughing]
- By all means, my beauty.

01:29:39.718 --> 01:29:44.381
Give Peter Pan
your precious thimble.

01:30:03.906 --> 01:30:06.568
This belongs to you...

01:30:08.010 --> 01:30:10.069
and always will.

01:30:32.599 --> 01:30:35.328
Ohh.

01:30:40.239 --> 01:30:43.605
That was no thimble.

01:30:43.675 --> 01:30:47.042
That was her hidden kiss.

01:30:47.112 --> 01:30:50.604
<i>[Thunder Rumbling]</i>

01:31:05.595 --> 01:31:07.688
Brace yourselves, lads.

01:31:07.764 --> 01:31:10.198
'Tis a powerful thing.

01:31:10.266 --> 01:31:14.201
Pan, you're pink!

01:31:17.272 --> 01:31:20.639
[Bell Ringing]

01:31:29.350 --> 01:31:31.284
Split my infinitives!

01:31:31.352 --> 01:31:35.378
- [Yelling]
- [Screaming]

01:31:35.455 --> 01:31:37.821
- [Screams]
- [Laughing]

01:31:52.871 --> 01:31:56.806
[Laughing]

01:31:56.874 --> 01:31:59.934
[Boys Cheering]

01:32:09.319 --> 01:32:12.686
No! I have won!

01:32:12.756 --> 01:32:16.350
[Peter Laughs]
Whoo-hoo!

01:32:16.425 --> 01:32:19.792
<i>[Hook Groaning]</i>
You... are old.

01:32:19.862 --> 01:32:22.456
[Grunts]
But I won!

01:32:26.034 --> 01:32:28.525
Old.

01:32:29.871 --> 01:32:32.533
And alone!

01:32:32.607 --> 01:32:36.667
- Alone.
- [Hook Screaming]

01:32:36.744 --> 01:32:40.703
- No! I won! I won!
- [Crocodile Roars]

01:32:40.781 --> 01:32:43.045
- [Gasps]
- Done for.

01:32:44.184 --> 01:32:45.844
Happy thoughts.
Happy thoughts.

01:32:45.918 --> 01:32:49.547
Ripping! Killing! Killing!
Choking! Lawyers! Dentists!

01:32:49.622 --> 01:32:51.522
[Chanting Together]
Old! Alone! Done for!

01:32:51.591 --> 01:32:53.559
[Whining]
<i>Old.! Alone.! Done for.!</i>

01:32:53.626 --> 01:32:56.025
<i>Old.! Alone.! Done for.!</i>
Pus!

01:32:56.094 --> 01:32:58.119
Uh, children's blood.
Puppies' blood.

01:32:58.196 --> 01:33:01.222
- Old! Alone! Done for!
Old! Alone! Done for!
- <i>Disease.! Scabs.!</i>

01:33:01.299 --> 01:33:04.291
Kittens dashed on spikes! No!
[Shouting Continues]

01:33:04.369 --> 01:33:08.134
- <i>Old.! Alone.! Done for.!</i>
- White death! Black death!

01:33:08.205 --> 01:33:10.696
- <i>Any death.! A nice cup of tea.!</i>
- Old! Alone! Done for!

01:33:10.775 --> 01:33:14.006
<i>Old.! Alone.! Done for.!</i>
<i>Old.! Alone.!</i>
Old. Alone.

01:33:14.078 --> 01:33:16.045
Done for!

01:33:18.615 --> 01:33:20.879
Done for.

01:33:26.889 --> 01:33:30.256
[Imitating Hook]
Brimstone and gall!
Silence, you dogs!

01:33:30.325 --> 01:33:33.226
Or I'll cast anchor in you.

01:33:33.295 --> 01:33:36.991
[Cheering]
We won! We won!

01:33:37.065 --> 01:33:40.228
Ready to cast off?
[Together]
Aye. Aye, Captain.

01:33:50.844 --> 01:33:53.779
Oh, the cleverness of you.

01:33:59.185 --> 01:34:01.346
[Whistles]

01:34:49.763 --> 01:34:52.493
[Clock Chiming]

01:35:08.881 --> 01:35:10.815
<i>[John]</i>
<i>Mother.</i>

01:35:16.221 --> 01:35:18.154
Nana.

01:35:22.160 --> 01:35:25.618
[Gasps, Sighs]

01:35:25.696 --> 01:35:27.788
Let us break it
to her gently.

01:35:33.103 --> 01:35:35.537
[Gasps]

01:35:35.605 --> 01:35:39.005
[Gasps]
Oh, Nana.

01:35:41.377 --> 01:35:43.937
I dreamt my little ones
had come back.

01:35:48.516 --> 01:35:50.643
I dreamed they were asleep...

01:35:52.520 --> 01:35:54.681
in their beds.

01:35:56.558 --> 01:35:58.923
But they will never come back.

01:36:06.934 --> 01:36:11.700
<i>[Narrator]</i>
<i>They did not understand</i>
<i>how she could not see them.</i>

01:36:11.771 --> 01:36:17.038
<i>But, you see, she saw them in their beds</i>
<i>so often in her dreams...</i>

01:36:17.109 --> 01:36:20.737
<i>that she thought this was just</i>
<i>the dream hanging around her still.</i>

01:36:23.481 --> 01:36:25.415
[Gasps]

01:36:30.588 --> 01:36:33.489
<i>Hello, Mother. It really is us.</i>

01:36:33.557 --> 01:36:36.253
[Sighs]
<i>Michael.</i>

01:36:36.327 --> 01:36:38.487
<i>John.</i>
<i>Wendy.</i>

01:36:38.561 --> 01:36:41.325
We're back.
[All Laughing]

01:36:41.397 --> 01:36:44.161
George, come quickly!

01:36:44.234 --> 01:36:46.896
<i>I'm coming.! What is it?</i>

01:36:54.977 --> 01:36:59.413
<i>We're back, Father.</i>
<i>Did you miss us?</i>

01:37:03.184 --> 01:37:05.118
You're back.

01:37:07.288 --> 01:37:10.017
Good. Excellent.

01:37:10.090 --> 01:37:12.888
Well done.

01:37:30.208 --> 01:37:32.574
[Sobbing]
Oh, my angel.

01:37:36.347 --> 01:37:38.871
Of course I missed you.

01:37:48.624 --> 01:37:50.922
[Sobbing Continues]

01:37:50.993 --> 01:37:53.985
<i>All right, boys, follow me.</i>
<i>Get your hands off that wallpaper.</i>

01:37:54.063 --> 01:37:57.931
Now, come on in.
The silliest thing.
These young gentlemen say that...

01:38:03.938 --> 01:38:05.963
You're back.

01:38:10.244 --> 01:38:12.235
<i>[Squealing]</i>

01:38:13.914 --> 01:38:17.645
[All Laughing]
Ohhh.

01:38:19.152 --> 01:38:22.644
Mother, Father,
I would like to introduce
the Lost Boys.

01:38:22.722 --> 01:38:24.656
Hello.
Hats.

01:38:26.159 --> 01:38:28.218
May I keep them?

01:38:32.397 --> 01:38:34.331
Well, l-l...

01:38:36.435 --> 01:38:39.835
I mean, the expense.

01:38:39.904 --> 01:38:43.203
Think of the neighbors.

01:38:45.476 --> 01:38:48.843
Dash the neighbors!
[Laughs]

01:38:48.913 --> 01:38:52.006
And dash the expense!
[Laughs]

01:38:52.082 --> 01:38:54.516
Welcome to the family, boys.

01:38:54.584 --> 01:38:57.280
[Cheering]
Thank you, thank you,
thank you, thank you.

01:38:57.354 --> 01:39:00.345
<i>[Cheering Continues]</i>

01:39:00.422 --> 01:39:03.823
Will this help the expense, Father?

01:39:07.363 --> 01:39:11.492
[Gasps]
Anyone for a pony ride?
[Cheering]

01:39:13.034 --> 01:39:15.525
I'm Tootles.
Tootles, darling.

01:39:15.603 --> 01:39:18.436
- I'm Curly.
- <i>Curly, darling.</i>

01:39:20.607 --> 01:39:22.802
And what's your name?

01:39:22.876 --> 01:39:25.106
Nibs. I plan the battles.

01:39:25.178 --> 01:39:27.612
Would you like
a mother, Nibs?

01:39:28.715 --> 01:39:30.648
Yes.
Oh!

01:39:32.284 --> 01:39:36.220
What is the matter, child?
I couldn't find the house.

01:39:36.288 --> 01:39:40.986
And now everyone has
a mother, except me.

01:39:41.059 --> 01:39:43.857
[Chattering]

01:39:46.498 --> 01:39:49.058
Is your name Slightly?

01:39:49.134 --> 01:39:51.260
Yes.

01:39:51.335 --> 01:39:54.532
Then I am your mother.

01:39:54.605 --> 01:39:56.539
How do you know?

01:39:56.607 --> 01:40:00.201
I feel it in my bones.

01:40:00.276 --> 01:40:02.938
Mother!

01:40:03.012 --> 01:40:05.503
George! Mary! I have a son!

01:40:06.082 --> 01:40:08.516
<i>[Narrator]</i>
<i>There could not have been</i>
<i>a lovelier sight,</i>

01:40:08.584 --> 01:40:10.551
<i>but there was none to see it...</i>

01:40:10.619 --> 01:40:13.884
<i>except a strange boy who</i>
<i>was staring in at the window.</i>

01:40:13.955 --> 01:40:16.947
<i>Peter Pan had countless joys...</i>

01:40:17.025 --> 01:40:20.051
<i>that other children</i>
<i>can never know,</i>

01:40:20.128 --> 01:40:22.891
<i>but he was looking</i>
<i>at the onejoy...</i>

01:40:22.963 --> 01:40:26.262
<i>from which he must be</i>
<i>forever barred.</i>

01:40:28.235 --> 01:40:31.692
To live would be
an awfully big adventure.

01:40:34.073 --> 01:40:37.042
[Chattering]

01:40:37.110 --> 01:40:39.101
[Blowing Raspberry]

01:40:42.014 --> 01:40:44.676
** [Violin]

01:40:51.189 --> 01:40:53.123
Peter!

01:40:55.059 --> 01:40:58.460
You won't forget me, will you?

01:41:00.031 --> 01:41:02.624
Me? Forget?

01:41:02.699 --> 01:41:04.633
<i>Never.</i>

01:41:20.816 --> 01:41:23.249
Will you come back?

01:41:26.688 --> 01:41:30.021
To hear stories... about me.

01:41:30.091 --> 01:41:32.786
[Chuckles]

01:41:46.906 --> 01:41:51.740
<i>[Narrator]</i>
<i>But I was not to see</i>
<i>Peter Pan again.</i>

01:41:51.810 --> 01:41:55.371
<i>Now I tell his story</i>
<i>to my children,</i>

01:41:55.447 --> 01:41:58.280
<i>and they will tell it</i>
<i>to their children...</i>

01:41:58.350 --> 01:42:01.285
<i>and so it will go on.</i>

01:42:01.353 --> 01:42:04.014
<i>For all children grow up...</i>

01:42:06.390 --> 01:42:08.324
<i>except one.</i>

01:42:11.794 --> 01:42:14.024
[Peter Laughs]

